    public class PwFloorIdMapLocationInterceptor
extends PwLocationInterceptor
    Provides a floorIdMap to store mapIndex key and PwFloorId, and put the PwFloorId along with PwLocationInterceptor.KEY_EXTRA_MAP_INDEX
